  minimal  energy.)     is  the  state  that   diagonalizes  the  field
Hamiltonian () at a  given moment of time 
.  Alternatively, it  can be shown that the
Hamiltonian  diagonalization vacuum  is the  state that  minimizes the
energy    at .   It directly
